I normally only use complete heal the others are to save folks if something gets messed up. the break over point for me is if i expect to be  healing 2k damage per heal<br>
<br>
celestial 225 mana 750 heal<br>
complete 400 mana <br>
<br>
so celestial  is about as effective if i expect to  be healing 1.5 k so complete really begins to pull away mana wise 2k heals.<br>
