<br>
I agree about not competing with clerics for healing.  If there is a cleric in my group I do my best not to step on his or her toes.  Sometimes I do get a little nervous when I see a party member's health vanish to almost nothing.  On those occasions I'll cast Chloroblast (a relatively small heal with short casting time) to keep them alive while the cleric is trying to get off a bigger heal.<br>
<br>
And yes, Azhrai, that was a high elven cleric.  How did you know? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
